data.description: Charming home offers 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. This beautiful home is situated on a quiet Cul-de-Sac street. Great floorplan, comfortable kitchen, spacious bedrooms, and a very nice private backyard. Backyard perfect for entertaining. Central AC. Absolute must see! Bonus room for more living space. This ideal location offers great schools nearby, and shopping enthusiasts will appreciate the easy access to numerous shops just a short drive away. This home is perfect for any first time home buyer or investor and wont last long. Don't miss your chance to make this house your family's home for many years to come.
